divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home testing my new digital camera taking pics of anything. I took some pics of clouds for fun and never really looked at them until tonight when i was clearing stuff off my hard drive. I dont remember seeing or hearing anything strange. It looks strange to me but it might just be one of those steath aircraft? I dont know why it says am I must not have set the time it was in the afternoon.
